<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - SSAutomation Solutions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <style>
        /* General styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .header, .nav, .footer {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #004080; /* Dark blue background */
            color: #ffffff; /* White text */
        }
        .nav {
            background-color: #d3d3d3; /* Light gray background */
            color: #ffffff; /* White text */
        }
        .header .title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
        }
        .nav .logo {
            background-color: #ffffff; /* White background for logo */
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .nav .logo img {
            height: 50px;
        }
        .nav .buttons a {
            color: #66a3ff; /* Light blue text */
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            background-color: #333333; /* Light black background */
            border: 2px solid #ffffff; /* White border */
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .nav .buttons a:hover {
            background-color: #000000; /* Darker background on hover */
            transform: scale(1.1); /* Increase size on hover */
            color: #ffffff; /* White text on hover */
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .images-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .images-container img {
            width: 45%;
            height: auto;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .images-container img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .content {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .content:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #004080; /* Dark blue color */
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .footer {
            justify-content: center; /* Center align text */
            text-align: center; /* Center align text */
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #004080; /* Dark blue background */
            color: #ffffff; /* White text */
        }

        /* Media Queries */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header, .nav {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .nav .buttons {
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
            .nav .buttons a {
                margin: 5px 0;
            }
            .images-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .images-container img {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- First Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <div class="title">Cage Inspection</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Second Header -->
    <div class="nav">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="images/SSA_logo.png" alt="Logo"> <!-- Replace with your logo -->
        </div>
        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="cage.html">Cage</a>
            <a href="database.html">Database</a>
            <a href="https://origin-www.ssautomation.in/">About</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="images-container">
            <img src="images/images11.jpg" alt="SSAutomation Solutions Image 1"> <!-- Replace with your image -->
            <img src="images/images33.jpg" alt="SSAutomation Solutions Image 2"> <!-- Replace with your image -->
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>About SSAutomation Solutions Pvt. Ltd.</h2>
            <p>SSAutomation Solutions Pvt. Ltd. is a leading provider of cutting-edge automation solutions, specializing in the inspection and monitoring of cage production. Our innovative technologies ensure the highest standards of quality and efficiency, making us a trusted partner for industries worldwide. With a commitment to excellence and a focus on continuous improvement, we help our clients achieve operational excellence and competitive advantage.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 SSAutomation Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
